description:
Britain and Ireland's Next Top Model - Cycle 9, Episode 1




Dannii Minogue joins host Elle Macpherson and Tyson Beckford on the judging panel as 28 hopefuls begin their battle for a modelling contract with a leading agency. The girls pull out all the stops to make a good first impression at boot camp and progress to the next stage of the competition, but only half of them will survive the cull.
